<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
<BLOCKQUOTE><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><HR>* If you or your group do less than half of the damage to the monster, the pet gets between 25% and 50% of the experience, depending on how much damage it did.<HR></BLOCKQUOTE><P>I still have a problem with this, because this seems to be saying, that if you are in a group of 6, and the pet does more than half the damage, the pet gets 50% of the experience, and the 6 players split the remaining 50% between them (so you each get 1/12 of the total experience).<P>The old way, if the pet did more than half the damage - it got a share - ie, 1/7th of the experience. At least that was how I understood the lastest explaination.<P>I'm hoping he means, that if the pet does more than half the damage, it takes between a full share and one half of a share of the experience.
